<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Stomach2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Stomach,</orth> vb. to be angry at, to resent: <cit><quote>believe not all; or, if you must believe, s. not all,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 4, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>'tis not a time for private --ing,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 9</bibl></cit>.
